name: Openstreetmap data wrangling

# Wrangling OpenStreetMap Data

## Intro
In this project, I chose Austin, Tx in the [OpenStreetMap](https://www.openstreetmap.org/#map=5/51.500/-0.100) and used data munging techniques, such as assessing the quality of the data for validity, accuracy, completeness, consistency and uniformity, to clean the OpenStreetMap data.
